---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800/80 to-slate-900/90 border border-slate-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold gradient-text mb-8 text-center leading-tight">Digital Manifesto: Forging the Totem of a New Era with Links</h3>
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-12 h-12 text-4xl text-primary opacity-40">
        <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-300 text-lg md:text-xl italic leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
        <p class="font-medium">In the flood of information, <span class="text-white">each of us is a nomad holding fragmented traces</span>.</p>
        <p>EgoLinks melts digital relics scattered across <span class="text-primary font-semibold">15</span> platforms—blogs, playlists, code repositories, or crypto art—<span class="text-white font-medium">into a spiritual badge that belongs only to you</span>.</p>
        <p>Here, the dark interface is the rebel's parchment, the floating particles are the futurist's star map, <span class="text-white font-medium">and the arrangement of links is the topology of the soul</span>.</p>
        <p>When quantum notes resonate with AI poetry and paintings, when gene logs dance with galaxy totems, algorithms will decode the Morse code of manifestos, building tribal bonfires for lone travelers on the digital wilderness.</p>
        <p class="text-white font-medium">Your <span class="text-secondary">378</span> bookmarks need not sleep, your <span class="text-secondary">2145</span> fragments need not wander. Now they will converge into a sword of declaration that breaks through chaos, imprinting your personal epic on the data wilderness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-12 h-12 text-4xl text-primary opacity-40">
        <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a href="https://egolinks.online/register" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-primary/20 hover:bg-primary/30 text-primary border border-primary/30 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <i class="fas fa-feather-alt mr-2"></i>Create Your Digital Manifesto
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #673AB7, #FF7F50);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
</style>